This move would follow a similar decision by his namesake, Michael Douglas, who has been using his birth name throughout his career. The news has sparked discussions on Keaton's potential name change, with headlines appearing in various publications, including The New York Times, NBC News, and Variety. name: Sabalenka
summary: In the 2024 US Open, Aryna Sabalenka has emerged as a dominant force, reaching the semifinals for the fourth consecutive year. Her impressive performance has garnered attention, particularly her victory over Zheng, which secured her place in the semis. Despite a late-night finish, Sabalenka maintained her composure by getting a full eight hours of sleep. Sabalenka's success has been met with fan enthusiasm, as evidenced by her signature offer of free drinks for the crowd. Her journey to the semifinals has been closely followed by tennis enthusiasts, including Roger Federer, who witnessed her quarterfinal victory. The title clash between Sabalenka and Jessica Pegula in the women's final promises to be a thrilling spectacle on Saturday.

name: Daylight saving time
summary: Daylight Saving Time (DST) in the United States is coming to an end, with most states observing the switch back to Standard Time on the first Sunday of November. However, several states and territories, including Arizona, Hawaii, Puerto Rico, and the U.S. Virgin Islands, do not observe DST and will not be making any time adjustments. Efforts to permanently end DST have gained traction, with some states considering legislation to eliminate the practice. As a result, the time change may not occur in some states in the future. It is important to check local regulations to confirm the exact date and time for the end of DST in your area. Additionally, the arrival of fall is imminent, signified by the changing colors of leaves and the apple cider season.
